reviewText: One of my favorite workouts. Never had a problem with the DVD not working. !!! Highly recommend it. Great butt workout and plus cardio . Where's volume 2!

I can't give an opinion on the substance of Brazilian Booty Workout because my DVD player could not read the disc. I have bought many exercise DVDs from Amazon and have had no problems and to this date they still work in my player. Do not throw out the packaging and receipt if you decide to order this DVD, you may need to return it!!!
